Class CodeEvaluator.Result<R,H>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.spi.debugger.ui.CodeEvaluator.Result<R,H>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - The type of the result object
    H - The type of the result history item (CodeEvaluator.Result.DefaultHistoryItem can be used).
    Enclosing class:
    CodeEvaluator

    public static final class CodeEvaluator.Result<R,H>
extends Object
    A helper class managing the evaluator result. Use it when "resultsView" is used to visualize the result of evaluation.
